    {
      "type": "content",
      "content": {
        "title": {
          "english": "Requesting a Taxi",
          "arabic": "طلب سيارة أجرة"
        },
        "text": "To specifically ask for a taxi, you can use one of these phrases.",
        "examples": [
          {
            "arabic": "بغيت طاكسي",
            "english": "I want a taxi",
            "transliteration": "Bghit taxi"
          },
          {
            "arabic": "واش كاين شي طاكسي هنا؟",
            "english": "Is there a taxi here?",
            "transliteration": "Wach kayn shi taxi hna?"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "content",
      "content": {
        "title": {
          "english": "Giving Your Destination",
          "arabic": "ذكر وجهتك"
        },
        "text": "Once you have a taxi, you'll need to tell the driver where you want to go. Here are common destinations.",
        "examples": [
          {
            "arabic": "بغيت نمشي لـ[اسم المكان]",
            "english": "I want to go to [place name]",
            "transliteration": "Bghit nmshi l-[esm l-makan]"
          },
          {
            "arabic": "المحطة",
            "english": "The station",
            "transliteration": "L-maḥaṭṭa"
          },
          {
            "arabic": "المطار",
            "english": "The airport",
            "transliteration": "L-maṭar"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "content",
      "content": {
        "title": {
          "english": "Enquiring about the Price",
          "arabic": "الاستفسار عن السعر"
        },
        "text": "Always confirm the price before starting your journey to avoid any surprises.",
        "examples": [
          {
            "arabic": "شحال الثمن؟",
            "english": "How much is the price?",
            "transliteration": "Shḥāl taman?"
          },
          {
            "arabic": "شحال؟",
            "english": "How much?",
            "transliteration": "Shḥāl?"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
