        "title": {
          "english": "Inquiring about Time",
          "arabic": "الاستفسار عن الوقت"
        },
        "text": "Knowing how to ask about time is crucial for travel planning and scheduling services.",
        "examples": [
          {
            "arabic": "إمتى؟",
            "english": "When?",
            "transliteration": "Imta?"
          },
          {
